		  <div class="__pf" id="__pf"><div class="pf-236d18f9 sc-hwwEjo kIFSBP" data-pf-type="Body"><div class="pf-9bd49392 sc-kUaPvJ gjMMZr" data-pf-type="Layout"><div data-container="true" class="pf-25861e8a sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-57599370 pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-3f9a5539 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h1 mode="view" class="pf-87b4b717 sc-epnACN OoUPE" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-e65867b6 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">&nbsp;Can I Vape on the Plane?<br></span></h1><h2 mode="view" class="pf-81e813dc sc-hXRMBi dwAIae" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-47093719 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Will vaping on the plane land you in trouble?</span></h2></div></div></div><div class="pf-9ecb1aea pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-984ee539 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 mode="view" class="pf-fcfaf11f sc-gwVKww lmgwgQ" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-ad4a20f9 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Becky Spencer-Davies, 05/06/2019&nbsp;</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="pf-e257c7d2 pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-b855c2e5 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><p class="pf-2103fba7 dropcap--none sc-ebFjAB ebQNGs" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-aac9db3e sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">W</span><span class="pf-f3357b6f sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">ith holidays coming up you might be wondering, can I vape on the plane? This certainly is a question for those going long haul. If you are heading to America, Thailand, Australia or somewhere further from the UK you’ll no doubt be concerned how you’ll manage without your trusty vape. In UK airports you are unable to vape, this will mean that you’ll be going longer than just your flight time without a puff.<br></span></p></div></div></div><div class="pf-e7e6792e pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-ae847378 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 mode="view" class="pf-89b50d22 sc-gwVKww lmgwgQ" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-05a5be35 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">How do I find out if I can vape on the plane?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-e3e471b8 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-9e08d577 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Right here. No, you cannot vape on the plane. At all. Not even a cheeky under your coat stealth vape, or a nip to the loo. If you are caught vaping on the plane you will face a hefty fine, not a great way to start or finish your holiday.&nbsp;<br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-bbaa3ab7 sc-gwVKww lmgwgQ" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-549b227b sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Will vaping on a plane get me arrested?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-2397e719 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-4d5b7eb5 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">It depends on the context. If you have been found to tamper with the smoke detector or refused to comply when the cabin crew asks you to stop then you will get more than a fine. You could be arrested and removed from the flight. Depending on the country you are flying to and the incident you could be arrested and put in jail when you get to your destination. <br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-9ba074e6 sc-gwVKww lmgwgQ" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-e1261d0e sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Could I use a pod or discrete vape on the plane?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-97020e68 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-5d71949f sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">So you might not be blowing huge clouds but you are still breaking the law and risking a fine. However stealth you think you are being with your <a href="https://vapeandjuice.co.uk/collections/starter-kits" target="_self">pod vape device</a> you might not get your suspicious behaviour past the cabin crew. <br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-6117e046 sc-gwVKww lmgwgQ" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-3fa92864 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">What should I do if I can’t vape on the plane?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-b19d1cfb sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-977dccfd sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">It’s frustrating, we get it. But gone are the days when you could smoke on a plane. The best thing to do to get your nicotine fix is to use nicotine patches, gum or lozenges. These long flights are perfect for nicotine replacement therapy!<br></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-d56e6507 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 mode="view" class="pf-33c20f53 sc-gwVKww lmgwgQ" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-14888450 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">How do I avoid the temptation of plane vaping?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-3518c3be sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-59f1fd44 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">You are not able to store your device in your hold luggage, you have to take it on board with you. We suggest that you store your vape device and e-liquids in your hand luggage in the overhead locker. This way you avoid temptation and any possible pocket leaks. <br>&nbsp;<br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-b6899884 sc-gwVKww lmgwgQ" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-c2501073 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Where can I find more information?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-10449639 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-f484ef07 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Your airline should be up to date on their website with rules regarding smoking and the use of e-cigarettes. If you want a second opinion then check with the airline, but we are pretty sure that the answer to can I vape on the plane, is no. <a href="https://www.britishairways.com/travel/askbainter/public/en_gb?p_search_text=e%20cigarettes" target="_self">Read British Airways vaping policy here.</a><br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-8ce61024 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-a09b4ddf pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-9e7e18c9 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-3c3c3a6c pf-r pf-r-ew pf-r-ew--4 sc-jMMfwr hRRmvw" data-animation="pulse" data-pf-type="Shopify.Products">{% for product in collections['high-vg'].products  limit:4 %}<div class="pf-c"><div class="pf__shopify-product shopify__product-vertical"><a class="product__thumbnail" href="{{ product.url }}" style="height: 200px; width: 100%;">{% if product.featured_image != blank %}<img src="{{ product.featured_image | img_url: '270x200', crop: 'center' , scale: 2 }}" alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}" width="270" height="200">{% else %}<img src="https://apps.pagefly.io/static/media/Product.8ea9e282.svg" class="pf-placeholder-svg" width="270">{% endif %}</a><div class="product__info"><h3 class="product__info-title"><a href="{{ product.url }}" style="display: block;">{{product.title}}</a></h3><div class="product__info-price" style="color: black; font-size: 13px;">{%- assign compare_at_price = product.compare_at_price -%}
